Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候起  我就時常能看到奇怪的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那大概是被稱作是妖怪一類
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.74,0:01:42.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  你往哪踢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  危險  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.55,0:01:48.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏目摔下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  那邊是別人家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.56,0:01:53.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  痛痛痛痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.06,0:01:54.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:57.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  還好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.81,0:02:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  麻煩你撿下球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.22,0:02:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.43,0:02:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球  球…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:12.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這張臉  是夏目大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.85,0:02:15.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳在你身上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:20.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  追上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  這繩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來以前好像也有過這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帳交出來！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳  快交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.38,0:02:44.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉  吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:47.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓  貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被妖怪纏上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.04,0:02:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事做就跟著來了  你就這德行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老  老師  很難受啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蝴蝶  蝴蝶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把友人帳交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.02,0:03:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我…  很難受啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼啊夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.19,0:03:16.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是做什麼吧  蠢貓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.83,0:03:18.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟你說過我不是貓了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.29,0:03:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是以招財貓為憑依的暫時的形象
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.27,0:03:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你是保鏢吧  那就認真點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別把我當普通保鏢使
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了得到友人帳而在等你壽命終結
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:38.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用重新解釋  你這大福餅貓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:42.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  總有一天我要吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
