Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:53.37,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(800,540)}{\c&H0025000}友{\r}\N人\N帳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收留了無處可去  在親戚間被推來推去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是心地善良的藤原夫婦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:07.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志  吃飯囉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:08.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵吉還沒回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.08,0:04:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它沒來吃飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:17.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在外面吃過了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了它就會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.34,0:04:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:28.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  嘗嘗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.23,0:04:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個好吃  是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是百合根啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:36.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不給他們添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.28,0:04:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看見妖怪的事絕對要保密
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒回房間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.63,0:04:48.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我打得太用力了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:53.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓  貓咪老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇我啊  你去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.80,0:05:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.78,0:05:04.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼弄的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.05,0:05:09.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別拿你的髒爪子到處踩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  洗不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼啊  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.54,0:05:27.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.45,0:05:30.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我剛才打了你  鬧彆扭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  剛才是老師你不對嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俺回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.22,0:05:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:46.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻黑的是啥啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然這傢伙是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.60,0:05:54.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼  不是老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一目了然吧  呆子！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.43,0:06:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉盤這麼大的貓沒幾隻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這傢伙是變成老師的樣子了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的何在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.12,0:06:09.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  友人帳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:11.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.53,0:06:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇  糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:21.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  跑哪去了  那隻黑貓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  這麼黑可找不到那黑傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:42.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.49,0:06:44.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  友人帳…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人類晚上在外面晃很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:51.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且今晚的空氣好像跟平常不同
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再找一會  再讓我找一會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那上面有妖怪們重要的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.41,0:06:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻滾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  冷靜下來夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然友人帳被搶很讓人生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.72,0:07:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我感覺那隻黑貓沒有惡意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.67,0:07:12.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才鬆懈了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在吵吵鬧鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓別的妖怪知道友人帳被搶了會更麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.93,0:07:21.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  那道光
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是狐火
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狐火？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.50,0:07:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量不少啊  這是要去哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:37.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:38.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:42.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好像聞到  有人類的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老 老師  好重…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.59,0:07:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍一忍  用我的味道掩蓋過去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞錯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.68,0:07:56.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還想著是不是人  這是野獸的腥臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:59.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然說是腥臭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.65,0:08:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這麼高貴而偉大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  以前主人經常帶著人的味道回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  就是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人化成人的樣子去村裡玩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:12.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.24,0:08:14.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還帶些好吃的回來分給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.76,0:08:20.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的人類  跟他們扯上關係就沒好下場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.21,0:08:22.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是斑大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您這身姿何時看都是這麼美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？你是紅峰嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你認識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.10,0:08:42.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您正在用餐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那請務必分我一點殘羹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.46,0:08:49.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？這張臉好像在哪…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  夏目玲子！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.95,0:08:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呆子  聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  是夏目玲子的孫子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.02,0:09:03.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅峰  剛才那群妖怪是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那是森林裡的妖怪聚集起來開宴會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.57,0:09:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  你在這附近見過一隻叼著一疊紙的可愛黑貓沒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:13.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可愛？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.89,0:09:19.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  倒是有隻大頭肥貓往宴會場去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:20.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…肥貓？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:21.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那隻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:24.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅峰小姐  能帶我們去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.32,0:09:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認真的嗎  人類的孩子去了立刻就會被吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就裝成妖怪去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.90,0:09:36.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  我必須得找到那隻貓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:42.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這任性的眼神  的確是像玲子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.11,0:09:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您就是喜歡他這點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:47.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊  再廢話就吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.23,0:09:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我就帶你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.55,0:09:56.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是能順利裝成妖怪也行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.19,0:09:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果到時候你被認出來是人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:10:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當大家的下酒菜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.26,0:10:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係  拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:06.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又自作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:14.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！斑大人變成豆丁了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.01,0:10:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,酒是在這邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們又不是去喝酒的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.79,0:10:25.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  夏目少爺得化妝或是戴面具
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人也不能露出野獸的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:30.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟您很有名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:36.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目玲子把友人帳傳給了長得像她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶著野獸的少年這事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.05,0:10:40.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是到處都在傳的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.86,0:10:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.07,0:10:51.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  你想讓那孩子在家待多久？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:54.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊  哥哥也說他不願意…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你回來啦  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.36,0:11:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好  找到玲子阿姨的遺物了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲子阿姨…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的祖母啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這是什麼  塗鴉本？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.76,0:11:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她是個怪人  看來相當怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:14.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個扔掉也可以哦  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西留著也沒意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:21.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:25.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天生擁有強大妖力的祖母玲子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.86,0:11:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將打敗的妖怪的名字寫下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.17,0:11:29.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訂立了主從契約
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候  我一點都不知道友人帳和玲子祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:38.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.69,0:11:41.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人就以這副樣子去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.08,0:11:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:45.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.22,0:11:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.02,0:12:03.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  紅峰  來得真遲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.12,0:12:05.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.56,0:12:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不解風情  我化了個妝啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦呀  沒見過的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是我帶來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:16.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很好玩啊  也讓我們加入吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:19.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題  來來  喝酒喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:23.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？我說你  有點人類的味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:27.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  我想起主人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:33.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯  主人也老是帶著人類的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:34.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡人類的森林之主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.27,0:12:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他變成人的樣子去村裡玩的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩到捕狐狸的陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從被一個獵人救了之後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就經常變成人去見那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.19,0:12:51.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還為交到了人類朋友而雀躍不已呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那位大人妖力雖然強大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.22,0:12:57.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭腦卻不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:13:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然會想和人類交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.60,0:13:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  還跟那個夏目玲子比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:08.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  有誰在附近看到一隻黑貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.02,0:13:14.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多來談談那件事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到可惡人類封印主人的地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是復仇的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人將力量分給下等的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.85,0:13:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還讓我們住在這森林裡的大恩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚  我們就進行夜襲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類根本不足為懼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:40.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起進攻他們就不堪一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜襲是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人襲擊了家畜  所以被人類封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.35,0:13:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是終於找到封印地點了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那個高高的紅牆房子的地板下面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.21,0:13:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  也沒必要襲擊那房子裡的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒必要  不過看這些傢伙喝成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.34,0:14:07.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知會做出什麼事來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:09.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你  可別去多管閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.53,0:14:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個數量是無法輕易阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:19.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  你就別管他們了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.94,0:14:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正人類能做到的事也是有限的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:26.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:31.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還好  我能聽見你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.07,0:14:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能聽到他們的聲音  還有人類的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.61,0:14:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不分厚薄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就一點忙也幫不上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.17,0:14:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟玲子不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.67,0:14:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.26,0:14:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子真難懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.48,0:14:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您到底喜歡他哪一點？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感興趣的是友人帳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就趕緊把他吃掉  搶過來不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.46,0:15:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也能給我殺殺時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.81,0:15:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的一生很短暫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眨眼就過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我抓到它了  老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.26,0:15:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  這傢伙怎麼這麼老實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.70,0:15:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這隻黑貓會不會是故意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故意的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:32.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得它是想通過搶友人帳  把我們帶到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅峰  你辦得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:44.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感應一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試試
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:55.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是強大的妖怪被封印在某個憑依上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.89,0:15:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑依啊  這樣做很流行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？這妖氣… 很熟悉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.19,0:16:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  難道是主人？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什喵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:08.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.84,0:16:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可憐了  可惡的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被封印了卻還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.56,0:16:18.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高高的紅牆房子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:23.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候弄斷的繩子是這隻黑貓的結界嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅峰小姐  趕快通知大家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人這個樣子  誰都不會相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.03,0:16:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得把封印解開  恢復以前的樣子才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.18,0:16:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎麼做…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.58,0:16:42.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有個低級妖怪說這傢伙跟玲子比賽過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  聽說是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.91,0:16:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個  或許是因為名字被奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.52,0:16:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以它才無法打破封印
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.34,0:16:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把名字還給它的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.93,0:16:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過問題在於名字
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝在憑依裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.94,0:17:00.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳是不會自動搜索名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅峰小姐  主人的名字叫什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  我也只知道叫他主人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人  我一定會把名字還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請你幫忙阻止大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:21.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個  在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:22.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.63,0:17:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發  是要去襲擊人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒必要了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:29.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人已經回到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵  呆子  別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:33.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰知道主人的名字嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:35.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要知道了名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人類的孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.35,0:17:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  該死的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開他！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了  滾一邊去！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意聽  這其中應該會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會有知道主人名字的妖怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸追大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開夏目！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.40,0:18:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸追  我把名字還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.08,0:18:34.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:51.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.71,0:18:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狸追大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:54.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.12,0:18:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.80,0:18:58.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主…人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了  各位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.47,0:19:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你而能活動了的我  去找他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:38.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找重要的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.91,0:19:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  他已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.24,0:19:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的一生真短暫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.64,0:19:50.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有點明白為什麼大家會說我笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會搶友人帳？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:54.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回到森林
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪們正想為我去襲擊人類的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.71,0:20:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有力量阻止  就把你帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.29,0:20:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你應該能做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.81,0:20:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:10.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印你的也是人類吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你卻想要阻止妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:22.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不會再到人類的村子裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡很舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:30.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  人類的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.57,0:20:32.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.65,0:20:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了啊  黑貓咪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:51.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:54.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑貓咪真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.55,0:20:56.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這什麼意思！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.17,0:21:01.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你以為是靠了誰這次的事件才能解決的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  斑大人的傷也不礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.42,0:21:10.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是無法喜歡人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.16,0:21:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.32,0:21:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本想著為了斑大人  就找機會把你給吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻礙於主人的大恩不能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑大人  要不乾脆就跟我一起回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.04,0:21:30.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  我還是暫時待在這傢伙身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那一眨眼的功夫過去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:36.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你坦率起來還真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.07,0:21:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的煩惱是  小小的離別帶來的寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.35,0:21:57.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬間的邂逅與分別
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.64,0:22:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一個一個的刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.01,0:22:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想好好珍惜起來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:50.01,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(150,550)}融化在春天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:36.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫玄
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:40.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人  請幫幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.89,0:23:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是芝原野的石像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.43,0:23:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是有兩座的  還有一座怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.53,0:23:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠…  她已經…


